title: Newly Renovated 3 Bedroom/3 Bath With Panoramic Views !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
